{"tha-ap16:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap16:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap16:0.3":"4 Culapanthakattheraapadana ","tha-ap16:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap16:1.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap16:1.3":"Ganamha vupakattho so, ","tha-ap16:1.4":"himavante vasi tada. ","tha-ap16:2.1":"Ahampi himavantamhi, ","tha-ap16:2.2":"vasami assame tada; ","tha-ap16:2.3":"Aciragatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap16:2.4":"upesim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap16:3.1":"Pupphacchattam gahetvana, ","tha-ap16:3.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap16:3.3":"Samadhim samapajjantam, ","tha-ap16:3.4":"antarayamakasaham. ","tha-ap16:4.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap16:4.2":"pupphacchattam adasaham; ","tha-ap16:4.3":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap16:4.4":"padumuttaro mahamuni. ","tha-ap16:5.1":"Sabbe deva attamana, ","tha-ap16:5.2":"himavantam upenti te; ","tha-ap16:5.3":"Sadhukaram pavattesum, ","tha-ap16:5.4":"anumodissati cakkhuma. ","tha-ap16:6.1":"Idam vatvana te deva, ","tha-ap16:6.2":"upagacchum naruttamam; ","tha-ap16:6.3":"Akase dharayantassa, ","tha-ap16:6.4":"padumacchattamuttamam. ","tha-ap16:7.1":"Satapattachattam paggayha, ","tha-ap16:7.2":"adasi tapaso mama; ","tha-ap16:7.3":"‘Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap16:7.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap16:8.1":"Pancavisatikappani, ","tha-ap16:8.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap16:8.3":"Catuttimsatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap16:8.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap16:9.1":"Yam yam yonim samsarati, ","tha-ap16:9.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap16:9.3":"Abbhokase patitthantam, ","tha-ap16:9.4":"padumam dharayissati. ","tha-ap16:10.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap16:10.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap16:10.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap16:10.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap16:11.1":"Pakasite pavacane, ","tha-ap16:11.2":"manussattam labhissati; ","tha-ap16:11.3":"Manomayamhi kayamhi, ","tha-ap16:11.4":"uttamo so bhavissati. ","tha-ap16:12.1":"Dve bhataro bhavissanti, ","tha-ap16:12.2":"ubhopi panthakavhaya; ","tha-ap16:12.3":"Anubhotva uttamattham, ","tha-ap16:12.4":"jotayissanti sasanam’. ","tha-ap16:13.1":"Soham attharasavasso, ","tha-ap16:13.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap16:13.3":"Visesaham na vindami, ","tha-ap16:13.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap16:14.1":"Dandha mayham gati asi, ","tha-ap16:14.2":"paribhuto pure ahum; ","tha-ap16:14.3":"Bhata ca mam panamesi, ","tha-ap16:14.4":"gaccha dani sakam gharam. ","tha-ap16:15.1":"Soham panamito santo, ","tha-ap16:15.2":"sangharamassa kotthake; ","tha-ap16:15.3":"Dummano tattha atthasim, ","tha-ap16:15.4":"samannasmim apekkhava. ","tha-ap16:16.1":"Bhagava tattha agacchi, ","tha-ap16:16.2":"sisam mayham paramasi; ","tha-ap16:16.3":"Bahaya mam gahetvana, ","tha-ap16:16.4":"sangharamam pavesayi. ","tha-ap16:17.1":"Anukampaya me sattha, ","tha-ap16:17.2":"adasi padapunchanim; ","tha-ap16:17.3":"Evam suddham adhitthehi, ","tha-ap16:17.4":"ekamantamadhitthaham. ","tha-ap16:18.1":"Hatthehi tamaham gayha, ","tha-ap16:18.2":"sarim kokanadam aham; ","tha-ap16:18.3":"Tattha cittam vimucci me, ","tha-ap16:18.4":"arahattam apapunim. ","tha-ap16:19.1":"Manomayesu kayesu, ","tha-ap16:19.2":"sabbattha paramim gato; ","tha-ap16:19.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap16:19.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap16:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap16:20.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap16:20.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap16:20.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap16:21.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma culapanthako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap16:22.1":"Culapanthakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}